{"tid":2250954,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"泰國民眾傍晚到各鐵路站「快閃」示威","createTime":"2020-10-20T12:43:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-20T13:55:35.000Z","uid":227801,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"661e5cd1e05efe5c192ce99b0f94f81de101c39f","tid":2250954,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T12:43:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/international/player?newsId=409812\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D409812&d=h9s%2FmsO%2BhBO0acKdDJaYEVe0bVP%2BLlUkdLfYKyPPBhg%3D&h=cd688304\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D409812&h=cb2137a8\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/international/player?newsId=409812</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://images-news.now.com/newsimage/NewsImage/THAI-PROTEST-201020-20.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages-news.now.com%2Fnewsimage%2FNewsImage%2FTHAI-PROTEST-201020-20.jpg&h=3471740c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【Now新聞台】泰國反政府示威持續，示威組織呼籲民眾傍晚到各個空鐵及地鐵站「快閃」集會。<br />\n<br />\n大批民眾響應號召，傍晚六點在曼谷市內各個鐵路站附近，舉起三隻手指的抗議手勢及叫口號，之後散去。<br />\n<br />\n「自由青年」等示威團體在社交網站稱，如果政府仍不回應他們的訴求，周三會有「重大宣布」。<br />\n<br />\n總理巴育政府已同意下周舉行國會特別會議，希望有助化解政治危機。"},{"pid":"aed8a3bbd89baf80eb7aa2ece281cf5cefe597a5","tid":2250954,"uid":2054,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T12:44:15.000Z","msg":"和你塞<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"343224c2bd0c1d8bf18279486abd3fd13661702a","tid":2250954,"uid":38777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T12:54:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2225494af56f7861